                                <td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td><a href="viewtopic.php?p=45162&amp;sid=e181baa0ad2c6aae116fd6b5f1f47036#45162"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Wed May 26, 2004 5:13 am<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: Question - Beserker Spirit</span></td>
                                <td align="right" valign="top" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=45162&amp;sid=e181baa0ad2c6aae116fd6b5f1f47036"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>    </td></tr></table></td>
