                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Berserker Spirit is just a 200 point rune (slightly over one hit from a miner), with a 40 str buff.  That's all.  If you chain cast it, then you can just get one to land per 15 seconds, which isn't enough to stop your animation from getting slaughtered.
<br />

<br />
The one thing I can imagine is that you benefited from the lag.  It is a common occurence in zones that suffer from raid lag (Ssra comes to mind), that mobs hit very much slower when lag is bad.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
