                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Also, make sure you put a shield spell on the pet. If you are planning to spend time out there again (isolated zone) then stop by in the bazaar first and see if a mage is selling pet toys. Mage summoned armor helps the pet, the muzzle of mardu is a 10% haste, the belts give extra hit points and stat bonuses to the pets, and the blades/fists help damage (procs) and give more hit points. Shiny Bob will live a bit longer still.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
